{"tid":1116194,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"公司有個同事成日講廢話","createTime":"2019-04-19T18:02:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T18:24:00.000Z","uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e094ac5ce5aff5c7c4ce91bbf95eb14d0bc84ccd","tid":1116194,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T18:02:50.000Z","msg":"一班人吹下水 嘻嘻哈哈咁<br />\n唔算係排擠佢嘅<br />\n<br />\n但佢永遠係加把口嘅一個<br />\n次次一出聲 佢同其中一人講野<br />\n除咗回應佢嘅人之外 其他人都靜哂<br />\n<br />\n究竟邊緣人 同 講廢話<br />\n<br />\n邊樣係因邊樣係果<br />\n有時好想話佢知呢樣野 但唔熟 又好似無必要搞到面阻阻<br />\n<br />\nBtw佢已經係阿叔樣，但把聲好女 好無中氣 <br />\n 有時「哦～」一聲，好似女人呻吟，真係想打鑊佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20617406694c0bc87d08c3dcbf202555669de4a4","tid":1116194,"uid":208726,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T18:10:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac7b68aabd386542ec0140b4e4b2f7d0be297503","tid":1116194,"uid":116614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T18:16:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9f577541906b4c26f69bfecc13fada4b3c6a46","tid":1116194,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T18:17:54.000Z","msg":"sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f88378f13866dfbce1dde85886aa58225d72711","tid":1116194,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac7b68aabd386542ec0140b4e4b2f7d0be297503","tid":1116194,"uid":116614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T18:16:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T18:24:00.000Z","msg":"巴打邊區返工"}]}